Four months ago!</translation></item_16>

column7: なぁにあんたに鉄砲で撃たれたのを覚えとるんじゃ

column4: わぁまた！４か月も前のことを

column6: <item_0><text>138</text></item_0><item_1><text>139</text></item_1><item_2><text>．．．どめっ！</text><translation>...Dome!</translation></item_2><item_3><text>鉄砲は捨てた</text><translation>Put the musket away</translation></item_3><item_4><text>おーい大将まちがって犬を撃ちなさんなよーーぉ</text><translation>Hey, Major, you're mistaken. column6: <item_0><text>世の中虎穴に入らずんば虎子を得ずだ</text><translation>In the world, if you don't enter the tiger's den, you won't get the tiger's cub.</translation></item_0><item_1><text>旅行してぇだけだろ！！</text><translation>Just travel, okay!!</translation></item_1><item_2><text>先生はそれをお前に教えたい</text><translation>Mr. is eager to teach you that.</translation></item_2><item_3><text>お前が石橋を叩いて渡るのが好きなのはわかるが</text><translation>I understand that you like to cross the bridge by hitting it.</translation></item_3><item_4><text>だから先生が温泉に行ってる間天文部を頼む</text><translation>So, I'm asking you to help the astronomy club while Mr. is at the hot springs.</translation></item_4><item_5><text>～</text><translation>～</translation></item_5><item_6><text>１</text><translation>1</translation></item_6><item_7><text>まあ聞け</text><translation>Okay, listen up.</translation></item_7><item_8><text>！？</text><translation>!?</translation></item_8><item_9><text>ちょっ</text><translation>Just a moment.</translation></item_9><item_10><text>なんで関係ない部活の手伝いなんかー</text><translation>Why should I help with a club that has nothing to do with me?</translation></item_10><item_11><text>！</text><translation>!</translation></item_11><item_12><text>．．．</text><translation>...</translation></item_12><item_13><text>お前には夏休みの間</text><translation>During the summer break, I'll ask you to help the astronomy club.</translation></item_13><item_14><text>我が天文部の手伝いをしてもらう</text><translation>I'll ask you to help the astronomy club.</translation></item_14>
